summary: Instantly become a god having power beyond what you would dream of having...
descriptionHtml:
DESCRIPTION
Ok so this file basically gives you everything you need to have the ultimate character in the DEFAULT VERSION OF SKYRIM. I will release a Dawnguard and Dragonborn update as soon as I can.

INCLUDES
Instant level 100 in all skills and all perks added
Gives all Daedric armor and weapons
Gives you one billion gold
Gives you 15 filled black soul gems
Gives you an item holding each enchantment (for you to disenchant and receive)
Gives you all ingredients (to taste and learn)
Adds all spells
Adds all shouts
Gives 60 dragon souls for the shouts
Changes you level to 81

INSTALL
Download manually
Go to where Skyrim is installed (should have TESV in it)
Place godmode.txt there

USE
Once installed go on Skyrim and open the console
type in "bat godmode"
Simple as that
author: IceflameV
